                "invention-title": [
                    "Ocean vessel energy co-supply system",
                    "一种远洋船舶能源联供的系统"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the technical field of multi-energy utilization, and provides an ocean vessel energy co-supply system. The system comprises a ship cooling system, a ship heat supply system, a first reversible solid oxide fuel cell, a second reversible solid oxide fuel cell, a ship wind power generation system, a heavy oil hydrogen doping system and a ship power system, the first reversible solid oxide fuel cell electrolyzes seawater to produce hydrogen in an SOEC mode, generated oxygen can be supplied for fishing operation, hydrogen can be doped with heavy oil, and high-quality fuel oil is provided; the second reversible solid oxide fuel cell utilizes the hydrogen to generate power in an SOFC mode, so that the dependence of the ship on fuel oil can be reduced; condensate water can provide guarantee for production and life. According to the system, the cost can be reduced, greenhouse gas emission is reduced, pollution to the ocean is reduced, and the energy utilization rate is increased."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本公开属于多能源利用技术领域，提供了一种远洋船舶能源联供的系统。该系统包括船舶冷却系统、船用供热系统、第一可逆固体氧化物燃料电池、第二可逆固体氧化物燃料电池、船舶风力发电系统、重油掺氢系统和船舶动力系统；第一可逆固体氧化物燃料电池在SOEC模式下电解海水制氢，产生的氧气可为捕鱼作业供氧，氢气可进行重油掺氢，提供高品质燃料油；第二可逆固体氧化物燃料电池在SOFC模式下利用上述氢气进行发电，可减少船舶对燃油的依赖；冷凝水可为生产生活提高保障。本公开的系统可降低成本，减少温室气体排放，降低对海洋的污染，并提高了能源利用率。"
                }
            ]
